ue to strict Olympic security measures.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several tourists\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"security barriers\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"police checkpoints\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"blocked streets\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"closed restaurants\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"strict Olympic security measures\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recommended Videos Many popular landmarks restricted access for Parisians and tourists unless they had a pre-approved QR code that justified the need for walking within the perimeter.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Recommended Videos\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"Many popular landmarks\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"a pre-approved QR code\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the perimeter\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheKPRC 2 Paris crewfound one of the best ways to avoid all the traffic and blockages is by taking the metro.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974252205, \"rank\": 2.5746322038427384e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best ways\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"all the traffic\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"blockages\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the metro\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\":